{"tid":31450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《明報》高層　劉進圖被斬命危","createTime":"2016-12-09T16:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T17:02:03.000Z","uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2b7165c565d4739dacb475828ea37d825adba48","tid":31450,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:29:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20140227/18639749\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20140227%2F18639749&d=1wAclGq59pQwgyJdjS%2BgeEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=3889184f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20140227%2F18639749&h=efb0d054\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20140227/18639749</a><br />\n<br />\n本報訊】《明報》前總編輯、現任網絡營運總裁劉進圖，昨晨駕車前往西灣河鯉景灣吃早餐，泊車後準備入咪錶時，兩名刀手同騎一輛電單車馳至，車尾男子手持牛肉刀步近，從後向他揮刀狂斬，劉身中六刀倒地，搶救後危殆。各界譴責兇徒暴行，《明報》懸紅100萬元緝兇。<br />\n<br />\n呢100萬有人攞到未？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a259deaf29913f15b201b776bb2eb6c3b244e760","tid":31450,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:33:16.000Z","msg":"唔咪拉曬食曬死貓啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n訓咗幾耐"},{"pid":"270f8fc41d412f0fb014944fca67019e1cdfa011","tid":31450,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:02:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔咪拉曬食曬死貓啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n訓咗幾耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係幕後黑手呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}